Description: Turns a single ggplot-like formula string into a small Shiny
    application. The package generates user controls from placeholder tokens,
    completes the expression with current inputs, renders plots, shows the
    generated code, supports uploaded '.csv' and '.rds' datasets, and can
    export a standalone Shiny app that uses the same runtime helpers.
